OL,3,C'It's scarred me, just you can't see
OL,4,Cmy scars' - one woman's story of abuse
OL,6,FIn Sunderland many victims of abuse
OL,7,Fturn to Wearside Women in Need for
OL,8,Fhelp.JEmma Duffy, project development
OL,9,Fofficer at the charity welcomed the
OL,10,Frecommendations as promising.
OL,12,F"Whatever's been happening for the
OL,13,Flast 40 years, unfortunately hasn't
OL,14,Fbeen decreasing it at the rate we
OL,15,Fwould want and we need to stop looking
OL,16,Fat violence against women and girls,
OL,17,Fas it says in the report, as if it's
OL,18,Finevitable," she said. "We can prevent
OL,19,Fthis, we can create a zero tolerance
OL,20,Fapproach and for that we need a lot of
OL,21,Fpeople to do so and help us do that."
