OL,3,C'It's scarred me, just you can't see
OL,4,Cmy scars' - one woman's story of abuse
OL,6,FSenior police officers are calling for
OL,7,Fgovernment intervention in the
OL,8,F"overwhelmed" criminal justice system.
OL,10,FThey want to see the creation of a
OL,11,FNational Centre for Public Protection
OL,12,Fto support police forces with
OL,13,Fspecialist knowledge and training.
OL,15,FChange like this is needed, according
OL,16,Fthe charity which sees a rise in
OL,17,Fvictims coming for help every year.
OL,19,FViolence against women and girls is
OL,20,Fnow officially classed as a national
OL,21,Fthreat.
